ing: 1 (8.5 ounce) package dry corn muffin mix
des: "A very easy orange cornbread Johnny cake to serve warm with butter and maple syrup. It's excellent with bacon or ham and leftovers are also good cold as a snack."
ins:
Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C). Lightly grease an 8x8 inch baking pan.
In a large bowl, stir together muffin mix, egg, milk and orange zest. Pour batter into prepared pan.
Bake in preheated oven for 20 to 25 minutes, until golden brown.
